<dl id="n54120a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n54" href="#n54120a">N54 (VI.B.45)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n54all.htm#n54120a"> 120(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 3 generations of M.D,</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">These medical men said, and it was generally believed, that it was not safe to entrust your health into the hands of a <mark>physician whose family had not been in the profession for at least three generations</mark>. <small> Carl Crow, <a name="CCMK" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CCMK"><cite title="source">Master Kung. The Story of Confucius</cite></a> (Sep 1937) 43</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
